reviewText: Love Narada but not very impressed with this video.

I thought it was a concert
Its still mike!!!

"Mr. Walden is an Incredible drummer and humorous in his explanation of styles & techniques."He covers a lot of really good stuff on his first Instructional dvd."I would highly recommend it to anyone who is serious on improving their drumming skills.
This should be a free video..... No real teaching. Really poor information in all sections. It is like a promocional video.
I really loved his approach to drumming and life.  I am going to buy the second volume.  GO BLUE!!!  Play on!
Detailed. The DVD gives you an inside look in what made Narada Michael Walden a great drummer. A Great DVD.
